RESTFUL ROUTES

NAME        URL         VERB         DISC.
============================================

INDEX       /dogs       GET         DISPLAY ALL DOGS

NEW         /dogs/new   GET         DISPLAY FORM FOR NEW DOGS

CREATE      /dogs       POST        ADD DOG TO DB

SHOW        /dogs       GET         SHOW INFO ABOUT ONE DOG


=============================================================
    CAMPGROUNDS
    
INDEX       /campgrounds        GET
NEW         /campgrounds/new    GET
CREATE      /campgrounds        POST
SHOW        /campground/:id     GET
=====================================

    COMMENTS
    
NEW         /campgrounds/:id/comments/new   GET
CREATE      /campgrounds/:id/comments               POST


